WEBVTT

00:00.534 --> 00:03.235
This looks like a job for Amy Adams.

00:03.554 --> 00:09.349
After months of speculation, the casting of Lois Lane in the new Superman reboot has finally been revealed.

00:09.967 --> 00:14.101
The three - time Oscar nominee has been cast to play the iconic Daily Planet reporter...

00:14.455 --> 00:17.076
...in director Zack Snyder's upcoming Superman reboot.

00:17.749 --> 00:23.313
Adams will co-star alongside British actor Henry Cavill who played Clark Kent aka Superman.

00:23.764 --> 00:28.464
Now in pre - production, look for Adams as the tough - edged journalist and Superman's love interest...

00:28.777 --> 00:32.671
...when Superman: Man of Steel hits theaters in December, 2012.

00:33.232 --> 00:35.819
Ken Lombardi, CBSNews.com.

